well-being.

38:57.635 --> 39:01.472 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: Tell me a
little bit about,
what's the relationship between
Australia

39:01.506 --> 39:03.107 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
and this tiny island nation?

39:03.141 --> 39:04.876 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
