39:04.909 --> 39:08.813 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
ANNA NEISTAT: Well, the
relationship is pretty,
pretty simple.

39:08.846 --> 39:13.117 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
At some point, when Australia
decided that
they are not going to accept
refugees who

39:13.151 --> 39:18.456 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
are arriving by boat, ostensibly
in order
to prevent people from dying at
sea and to

39:18.489 --> 39:22.493 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
