this offshore
processing.

39:22.527 --> 39:29.000 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
So Australia is now paying
hundreds of millions
of dollars per year for this
operation.

39:29.033 --> 39:32.937 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Obviously, it's a significant
part of Nauru's
economy.

39:32.971 --> 39:36.040 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
The island doesn't really have
much else.

39:36.074 --> 39:42.680 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And, in exchange, obviously,
Nauru gets some
employment opportunities, some
investment

39:42.714 --> 39:44.482 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
