off.

41:13.705 --> 41:18.976 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And now that it's off, I really
think it's
high time for Australia to stop
denying -- denying

41:19.010 --> 41:26.050 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
the undeniable and really start
closing down
this whole operation both in
Manus and in

41:26.084 --> 41:30.655 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Nauru and resettling people
either in Australia
or in an appropriate third
country.

